==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Protrusion
<hw>Pro*tru"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act of protruding or thrusting forward, or beyond the usual
limit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being protruded, or thrust
forward.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Protrusive</ent>⟦br⟧
